# Local AI Instructions Override

> This file overrides settings in `AI_INSTRUCTIONS.md` for local development.
> **This file is gitignored** - use it for personal/machine-specific preferences.

## How to Use

Add sections below to override corresponding sections in `AI_INSTRUCTIONS.md`.
The AI will use these values instead of the defaults.

---

## Deployment

**Mode**: Local (No Docker)

### Start Services

```bash
# Backend
cd services/backend
uv sync
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000

# Frontend
cd services/frontend
pnpm install
pnpm dev
```

### Database

```bash
# Local PostgreSQL
psql -U postgres -c "CREATE DATABASE your_project_db;"

# Or use SQLite for simple setup
DATABASE_DIALECT=sqlite
DATABASE_NAME=./dev.db
```

### Redis

```bash
# Local Redis
redis-server
```

